title: 1  Activity 01
text:
Hello I am currently tinkering with this document in r studio to see how it works. I hope this text stays.
Ok, this is actually really cool. I never realized how many different files went into creating a website.
Its interesting to see how almost every different page is its own file and how in addittion to that there are also even more files which tell R which files it needs to save to make the journal.
